    <description>Docotic.Pdf library can create, edit, draw and print PDF files.

The library is a fully managed assembly for .NET Standard 1.3, .NET 2.0 and later frameworks. The assembly has no external dependencies.

There are different types of licenses: for applications, for servers, cloud and unlimited. All licenses are royalty-free. 

Free time-limited licenses are available upon request.</description>
    <summary>Create, edit, draw and print PDF files in your application or web service with royalty-free Docotic.Pdf library. Fully managed assembly for .NET 2.0 and later frameworks. Has no external dependencies.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>http://bitmiracle.com/pdf-library/help/version-history.aspx</releaseNotes>
